isAccepted

                          java.lang.String type,
                          java.lang.String name,
                          int s)
Checks required expid/session/runtype/type/name selected by the user (treeBuildSubject build by the jtree selection) and passed values (from the dalog message)

Parameters:
expid - of the platform
session - of the experiment
runtype - of the experiment
type - of the component
name - of the component
s - severity in case passed severity id == -111, means message does not have a serverity payload item, and we do not have to filter based on severity id.
Returns:
true if accepted and false if not

isAccepted

public boolean isAccepted(org.jlab.coda.cMsg.cMsgMessage msg)
Expect specific payload items, that define the logical address of the sender, in the message to define if the message will be visualized. msg - cMsgMessage object
Returns:
